'''Aqqaṛ''' d azgen n [[akdu|wekdu]] n [[tawinest|twinest]] neɣ [[tasegla|tsegla]] neɣ n [[aglay (tusnakt)|uglay]]. Aqqaṛ yegda amaccaq yebṭan gar n wammas n twinest ( neɣ tsegla neɣ n uglay) de yal agaz deg tlisa n telɣa. 

Aqqaṛ yegda [[taseɣleyt]] yebṭa ɣef 2 [[Pi]] ( <math>r = \frac{c}{2\pi}</math> ).

== Aqqaṛ n twinest ==
Assaɣ gar n waqqaṛ <math>R</math> d tseɣleyt <math>L</math> n twinest d: <math>R=\frac L{2\pi}</math>.[[File:Sinilause1.jpg|thumb]]

I usiden n waqqaṛ <math>R</math> i twinest i yekkan ɣef 3 n wagazen <math>A,B,C</math> nezmer ad nessemres taftart-a :
<center>
<math>R=\frac a{2\sin\alpha}</math>,
neɣ <math>a</math> est la longueur <math>BC</math> et <math>\alpha</math> akat n [[tiɣmert|tɣmert]] <math>\widehat{BAC}</math> .
</center>

Ma ttwanefken 3 n wazagen s yimsidag-nsen <math> (x_1,y_1) </math>, <math> (x_2,y_2) </math> d <math> (x_3,y_3) </math>, nezmer daɣen ad nessemres taftart-a (voir [[asaduf n uwsi]] et [[Tajumma n ukeṛdis]]) :

